Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.93,0:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question has to do with prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And since September 8th is going to be a big unity prayer day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel compelled to participate in the prayer day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, in a group like this, with all of us together with intention of prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,could we raise the consciousness of the world by joining together on that day to pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a cause and effect relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By ourselves, we can't lift the level of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of humanity together by intention constantly raises the level of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone floating on the ocean gets lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But not by cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But by virtue of that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By your intention of what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you contribute to the overall field, and the field is what lifts people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we did it in a group, if I went to a group to pray, the intention of the group...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's numerical causality again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A group prayer is more efficacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More efficacious in raising the level of mankind than just individual prayer resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Group prayer is, yes, efficacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm glad you mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what is the date again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,September the 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,September the 8th is Unity Prayer Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had that on my list to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unity, annual Unity Prayer Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a powerful time for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an excellent time to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my question is, I'm an interpreter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak several languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And to work, I do it automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm able now to just witness the interpretation process and step back of it and just witness what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I started...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When I started reading and studying your material, I realized that it was good for me to start knowing something about meditation because I was clueless and I started working on the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So all of a sudden, one day I was driving and I realized for a second that there's no separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no out there and in the in here, and I felt a huge vertigo, like I need to hang on to and hold on to something because I felt like it was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I on the right path or I need a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're on the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditating when you're driving may not be the best deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's a reorientation because of the shift of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:05:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you go into a really incredible space, you may not be able to function for periods of time because where you are in space and people keep talking to the body and you've got nothing to do with the body and they think it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it has to do with reorienting yourself within a new context.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of strangeness disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep surrendering and praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,different glasses, very similar to wearing different glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can actually see better than you could before, but there's a reorientation and that's how you felt was that reorienting yourself to a shifted context.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, devotion and spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is devotion a quality of the spiritual will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is devotion a quality of the spiritual will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is devotion a quality of the spiritual will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it the same thing where I just forget about it and just keep doing what I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will is more like a stated intention, a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And devotion is more dedication and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When you combine the two, you have devotional non-duality, which is the book I'm finishing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have devotion to truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have devotion to truth, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives it power is not only intention, which can be just mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But also the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And devotion comes from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So the power of the heart then energizing the will and reason and intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you talk a lot about the 400s and the 500s, but between 500 and enlightenment is the 600s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you haven't mentioned much that I've heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you haven't mentioned much that I've heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you haven't mentioned much that I've heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any milestones in the 600s or things to let go of?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are, we're going to, we're doing the levels now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, we do the levels below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we go from 200 up to 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,From 600 up are the levels, specifically, formally, those of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sat Chittananda, Silent Bliss is at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem of how to get from 600 on up is infrequent because most people leave at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Some continue on, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But without motivation to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In 600, there is no motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is perfect, still, infinite, peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It would not come up that there is anything further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything you learned about it would probably be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is that which is, it does not seem possible to the ego that there is anything beyond 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everything is peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the body continues on or not is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite stillness, peace, and bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness, then, of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently, if it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently, if it's karmically attuned to do so, will continue on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And even rarer still, it will go on up higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually in the 700s, it will stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The best known sages of recent decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In 700 and something, it just stays there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it may start, extremely rarely, to move on up even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know when it's doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's a considerable discomfort at 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The nerves feel like they're on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The slightest thing that's out will make it quite severe, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're beyond personal karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what's holding you up is something from the collective consciousness of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To which you have ascribed due to humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At 800, you begin really sort of agonizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the dedication to continue on is what drives you through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At that level, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The information needed to transcend that level came in the form of finding a copy of a Buddhist text
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in the drawer of some foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And recalling that the Buddha said his bones felt like they were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, it became okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A group of us who are here today, some of us are here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,recently were around a swami who manifested jewelry and vibhuti, holy ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we want to know if this phenomenon of manifesting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,can happen when the teacher is below 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps more importantly, what is the purpose of manifesting these objects
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is indeed happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this really have to do with enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what all that has to do with enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have permission to do vibhuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Vibhuti calibrates over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Vibhuti calibrates over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,199.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Vibhuti calibrates around 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it has to do with confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really, it has to do, I've written a chapter on the cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,S-I-D-D-H-I-S.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are the phenomena, paranormal phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They begin to occur in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Become quite marked around 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Become almost continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're clairvoyant, clairaudient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is the common.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold a parking place in space in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you get there, there it is naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Various phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The so-called miraculous occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the consequences of kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If a person identifies them and begins to,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you have no control over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy does what it does under the direction of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what she's talking about is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with magic control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the egotism of the cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with claiming the cities
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of one's personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what impresses the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it, could it be then dangerous because it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To seek it for its own sake, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because to seek the cities is obviously an ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,attraction to the spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely want to be able to levitate, fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and all those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is obviously an attraction to the spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things are spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the miraculous is spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody is brought to have lunch with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at them and suddenly you get from the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they've brought you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They brought her because she has something terribly wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're hoping for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you look at the person with the love you feel towards all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and include them in the divinity of the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then either cures or doesn't cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they walk away cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is no person doing miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no performer of miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because the miraculous is the consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of divinity as the whole field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which then pulls forth the karmic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the apple falls from the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's karmically ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because you are causing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So we witness the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's always spontaneous of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no me causing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no this causing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So why jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. The glamour of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Glamour of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Theatrics of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I hide this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question that's along the lines
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with what we were just talking about, levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And in reading your material and your lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you state that the ego gets transcended
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,at level 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And something that keeps sticking to my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when you talked about Muhammad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,when he calibrated at 700
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and through almost a simplistic misinterpretation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sword of truth made a great fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was attacked by the Luciferic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as you get higher, you get attacked by that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the enemy of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because truth will reduce its dominion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're attacked by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, a book on truth versus falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how popular do you think that's going to make you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I waited until I was older.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When you tell the truth, quickly you leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm prepared, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So it has nothing to do with ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with an ego structure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,where something was offered, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in some sort of power, you know, control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more of an attack, you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that happened to Muhammad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he had a vulnerability
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Luciferic saw the energy and shot into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The same happens with alcohol intoxication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, demonic possession is very frequent in intoxication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he will take over the domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So when he had a temporal epileptic fit, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,his defense was down and the energy saw fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So it reversed mercy and turned evil into good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the classic Luciferic conversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The worship, you know, as Ben Laden says when he comes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we worship death, you worship life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that is not a traversable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not a traversable track.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not traversable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 180.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you traverse 180?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you what happened with this person,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,this entity here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In a very high space, beyond all personal karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,came out of nowhere a silent knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in the form of a temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I see it as a temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It came as a silent attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,via a non-verbal knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you realize you've transcended all personal karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no accountability,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,all power is yours, own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the knowingness said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Inasmuch as I couldn't see what the hell you want to do with power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be a drag and a nuisance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the self is all that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, very few people have been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so I saw who was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw the answers they gave, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called the Luciferian temptation, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It came to Jesus Christ in the Gethsemane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you advance, we haven't gotten that far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we get advanced to the levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we sort of look at, we did the levels below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're the most painful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when people get their foot out of the bear trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the higher levels will go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the very highest levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In transcending levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I go into the 600s, 700s, 800s,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and up, and I do in devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very limited audience for that kind of information,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm not going to take up the public's time with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But for people who are driven,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,driven in sort of a spiritual insanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're willing to go through hell to get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people will get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To have heard of the truth will then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,summon forth from the vibration and the aura
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to the knowingness of what to do with that temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you choose that which you already are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be denying the reality of what you are already,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to say, well, I choose power over others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very hot question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How about an easy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I want to thank you again
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for the incredible work you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You just helped me in my life in so many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This book, Truth vs. Falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,really forced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you put the caveat in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You do pay attention to the caveat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I paid attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I waited until I could handle it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't know if I still could,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just ouch, ouch, ouch, taking off band-aids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We got an email this week that said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,reading your book is ouch, ouch, ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like ripping off band-aids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See, people get so attached to their view
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's painful to let their view go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually wrote a letter of apology
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to President Bush
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because I felt so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a human being like you or I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably does the best he thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the situation he's in,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wouldn't take his job
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the money in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no matter what you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be made wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little disappointed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you have the Fortune 500 companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I work for Best Buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't listed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what they calibrate at?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we did some of them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's some,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but Best Buy wasn't listed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And not the one that you want to buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the one that you want to buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I work for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you work for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if you read literature like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you develop an intuitive eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know, that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.27,0:22:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And somebody will hand me a book
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think this calibrates?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A number shoots into my head already,
