Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.96,0:30:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you've got to become conscious of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.23,0:30:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.23,0:30:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In your investigation, what is the reluctance to surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.36,0:30:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you want to maintain control, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.80,0:30:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.80,0:30:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is your fear of letting go of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.98,0:30:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.98,0:30:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See, so you go inside questioning yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.51,0:30:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.74,0:31:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego survives on control, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.51,0:31:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to resist, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.19,0:31:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is not going to be happy that you want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.73,0:31:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Reduce its dominance in your life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.06,0:31:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a natural resistance of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.62,0:31:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is narcissistically sovereign.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.66,0:31:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to welcome your attempts to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.38,0:31:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It will find excuses, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.82,0:31:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.82,0:31:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.86,0:31:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.86,0:31:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.56,0:31:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you put that to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.59,0:31:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to our...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.59,0:31:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just normal resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.59,0:31:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it to John in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.68,0:31:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.68,0:31:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempt to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.68,0:31:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempt to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.68,0:31:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempt to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.58,0:31:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Address this to John.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.58,0:31:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the guy who does our videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.58,0:31:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.58,0:31:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.58,0:31:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.58,0:31:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.19,0:31:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.19,0:31:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.19,0:31:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.02,0:32:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.02,0:32:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to do with my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.02,0:32:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So much confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.01,0:32:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good job, and I think the company's integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.01,0:32:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the job's integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.42,0:32:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm not really contributing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.42,0:32:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.42,0:32:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm there eight hours a day, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.42,0:32:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.42,0:32:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.42,0:32:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.42,0:32:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.42,0:32:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.42,0:32:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.42,0:32:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.42,0:32:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.42,0:32:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.42,0:32:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.42,0:32:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.42,0:32:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.42,0:32:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.42,0:32:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.58,0:32:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.58,0:32:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.81,0:32:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.81,0:32:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wasting my time?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.81,0:32:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the one good thing is it allows me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.81,0:32:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come to all the talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.81,0:32:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.81,0:32:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But am I just wasting my life in this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.81,0:32:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on how you contextualize this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.81,0:32:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you contextualize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.81,0:32:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it being of service to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.97,0:32:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fulfilling the...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.97,0:32:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.97,0:32:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.97,0:32:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.97,0:32:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.97,0:32:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.97,0:32:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.97,0:32:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.10,0:32:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.10,0:32:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.10,0:32:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.10,0:32:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.10,0:32:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.10,0:32:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.10,0:32:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.10,0:32:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.10,0:32:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.10,0:32:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fulfilling your own potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.10,0:33:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just carrying forth responsibility towards yourself and your family for survival?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the best utilization of your skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.10,0:33:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, how you contextualize this value.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.10,0:33:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm not utilizing my potential, but I'm not sure what I should do, yet it's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.00,0:33:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.00,0:33:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.00,0:33:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the job is still integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.00,0:33:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.12,0:33:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the ego hates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.12,0:33:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.12,0:33:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.71,0:33:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,plenty of ego there too
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.31,0:33:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,okay so it's because you contextualize
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.03,0:33:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it as being ordinary mundane
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.83,0:33:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,pedestrians right
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.75,0:33:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to learn how to recontextualize
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.79,0:33:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,its value
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.47,0:33:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it serves you and the world
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.40,0:33:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it serves survival
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.74,0:33:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's an expression of your
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.42,0:33:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,value of your life to others
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.60,0:33:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a valuable cog in the wheel
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.66,0:33:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.31,0:33:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.39,0:34:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,not everybody has
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.69,0:34:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a life's work
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.81,0:34:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes people say
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.55,0:34:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.59,0:34:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't all be helicopter pilots
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.91,0:34:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.27,0:34:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,rescue swimmers
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.74,0:34:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,those are the heroes aren't they
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.13,0:34:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,most of us lead rather mundane lives
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.59,0:34:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.91,0:34:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we go to work every day
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.71,0:34:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and perform whatever skills we have
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.15,0:34:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.57,0:34:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.93,0:34:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can intuit an alternate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.89,0:34:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.48,0:34:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm saying through prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.58,0:34:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you say good lord
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.88,0:34:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.04,0:34:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you would wish me to do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.22,0:34:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,while I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.80,0:34:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with my time
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.84,0:34:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and my energy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.48,0:34:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and my body
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.10,0:34:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd surrender my life to thee oh lord
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so you pray for God's guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.90,0:34:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 12 step group
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.54,0:34:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the 11th step
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.64,0:34:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ask God for direction
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.98,0:34:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.50,0:34:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so you do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.91,0:34:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you meditate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.43,0:34:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ask God for direction
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.67,0:34:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.88,0:35:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing happens
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.63,0:35:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and then one day
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.19,0:35:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you pick up a magazine cover
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.49,0:35:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and flash
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.35,0:35:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.97,0:35:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.23,0:35:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you just got it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.89,0:35:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.79,0:35:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,cause and effect
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.59,0:35:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not volitional
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.43,0:35:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not linear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.13,0:35:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when you let go
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.91,0:35:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and forget about it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.07,0:35:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,trust that God will review
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.11,0:35:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.55,0:35:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.49,0:35:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,God's will is for you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.01,0:35:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.37,0:35:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then forget about it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.81,0:35:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.41,0:35:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.29,0:35:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and hits you in the head
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.99,0:35:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,like a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.63,0:35:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,step down a hole
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.55,0:35:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,oh that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.95,0:35:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,yep
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.21,0:35:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what I'm waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.81,0:35:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.27,0:35:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,may not be so dramatic
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.85,0:35:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,those also serve
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.45,0:35:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,who stand in wait
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.21,0:35:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.61,0:35:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.77,0:35:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.97,0:35:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.11,0:35:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.25,0:35:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.45,0:35:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.63,0:35:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for your patience
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.65,0:35:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,steadfastness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.12,0:35:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary steadfastness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.44,0:35:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.23,0:35:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.05,0:35:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,confused about something
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.31,0:35:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,actually two things
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.43,0:35:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,one is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.53,0:35:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since I've been a child
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.53,0:35:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been very worried
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.17,0:35:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,about the environment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.87,0:35:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm worried
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.55,0:35:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,about the environment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.71,0:35:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,environment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.81,0:35:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the environment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.73,0:35:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.23,0:36:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.41,0:36:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,looks pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.65,0:36:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the environment here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.35,0:36:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,oh are you talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.82,0:36:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's environment
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.72,0:36:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,pollution
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.46,0:36:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are you worried
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.40,0:36:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,about the world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.26,0:36:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.82,0:36:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,oh okay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.46,0:36:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.92,0:36:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's got to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.68,0:36:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,worry about something. So when I was a child, yeah, I tried to get my friends to take
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.28,0:36:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,care of things and critters. Yes. And now I have a cable show where I interview
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.08,0:36:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,people to show what's wrong with the environment, what we could do. And I start
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.66,0:36:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling sort of, hmm, I don't know if that's the right way to do it. I'm really
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.02,0:36:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,confused about whether or not, quote, the environment needs help or what the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.68,0:36:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,status of that is. Well, you see, you walk about in a state in which you see the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.60,0:36:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,sacredness, holiness, deservingness, and divinity of all that exists, and you treat
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.44,0:36:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it accordingly. And then what you do is a consequence of how you, how you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.57,0:37:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,understand it and grasp its significance. Yeah? You serve, you serve all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.30,0:37:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.88,0:37:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Expressions. Yes? So would you say that the environment is in trouble? Our planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.94,0:37:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be so general. You're asking, you know, is the planet in trouble? I don't know, I couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.36,0:37:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Is, uh, are there... The green stuff? Yeah. The animal stuff? Yeah. The oxygen? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody does what they can to contribute to the best of their comprehension of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.66,0:37:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,their function in the world. I mean, I see myself automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.81,0:37:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,picked up by the world. I mean, I see myself automatically picked up by the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.01,0:38:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,world. I see myself automatically picking up trash because I, I think, you know, it, it conceals the beauty of the world, you know? You find yourself automatically trying to serve the world as best you can just because that's your nature. It's not because of what you do, because of what you are, huh? Divers need a home, so you find yourself hanging in birdhouses. It's not to help the environment, that's, that's too much of a generality, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.49,0:38:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how it fumes and cars and emissions and smokestacks and greenhouse effects?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.91,0:38:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the cause of all that? We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.50,0:38:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is we? Me, yeah. No I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.36,0:38:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't. The totality of the population. We didn't have the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.43,0:38:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was born, there was only one-one billion people I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.46,0:38:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,1.5 billion. No, it's 6 billion. So the problem is not the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the pollution. The problem is people.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.88,0:38:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got so many people, that pollution is automatic. You can't do anything about...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.86,0:38:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the forests and the pollution and the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.12,0:38:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've got a population running like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.62,0:38:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem I see is this population.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.22,0:39:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the pollution of the ocean come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.47,0:39:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not people, lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.55,0:39:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Southern Asia, there is a cloud,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.36,0:39:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a dust cloud of haze, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.94,0:39:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,three miles high.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.06,0:39:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Three miles high.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.43,0:39:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because of the enormous population density.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.14,0:39:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to me, it's foolish to worry about the environment
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.16,0:39:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,without first taking care of the population problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.27,0:39:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.69,0:39:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.75,0:39:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're going to put your effort somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.73,0:39:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.17,0:39:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not put it where it counts?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.87,0:39:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.83,0:39:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be poor,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.26,0:39:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,have two kids instead of six.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.10,0:39:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.36,0:39:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want pollution,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.32,0:39:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,don't ask so many people to live by the Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.64,0:39:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I think the crux of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.33,0:39:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,environmentalism,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.15,0:39:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is population sprawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.03,0:40:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Population, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.31,0:40:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Population.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.69,0:40:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where it's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.75,0:40:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to have a living,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.05,0:40:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so they have to go through the Amazon forest in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.85,0:40:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to knock down the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.57,0:40:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have to have room for crops to raise the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.97,0:40:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the wild animals have to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.43,0:40:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But is the problem tearing down the Amazon forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.35,0:40:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the main source of oxygen?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.71,0:40:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Amazon forest is the source,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.87,0:40:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, 50% of the world's oxygen or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.91,0:40:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.32,0:40:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So why do the people keep pushing in and destroying the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.18,0:40:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's so many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.14,0:40:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got good intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.20,0:40:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you put it to the source instead of the effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.36,0:40:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The environmental impact is the effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.51,0:40:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.01,0:40:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.11,0:40:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred kids is going to make a lot of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.62,0:40:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten times more than ten kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.42,0:41:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all it wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.90,0:41:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's my take on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.68,0:41:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.20,0:41:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The goodwill of your efforts is, you know, laudable,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.50,0:41:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.63,0:41:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,While you have a party for the environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.85,0:41:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the bulldozers are relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.97,0:41:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant iron monsters are running,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.49,0:41:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,tearing down the Amazon forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.72,0:41:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the main source of oxygen on the planet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.03,0:41:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would seem like education,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.07,0:41:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,education of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.65,0:41:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.92,0:41:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.04,0:41:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not responsible to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.16,0:41:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's responsible to have big kids when you can only afford two.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.80,0:41:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So to somehow raise the educational level.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.40,0:41:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does that is education.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.24,0:41:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They found that education does more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.90,0:42:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Celtic, the Celtic tiger turnaround of Ireland
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.44,0:42:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,after two centuries of extreme poverty was due to free education.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.00,0:42:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher the education, the less the overpopulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.00,0:42:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the less the pollution, the less the environmental damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.30,0:42:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would start more to a central point of where it's all coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.14,0:42:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.18,0:42:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you're bandaging things without getting to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.82,0:42:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've got a central infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.06,0:42:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cure the infection, you don't have all these things to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.94,0:42:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.27,0:42:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see environmentalism running here, running there, running there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.63,0:42:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, the main faucet is still running, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.77,0:42:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just my take on it, but you asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.80,0:42:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.84,0:42:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for contributing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.17,0:42:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.67,0:43:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.55,0:43:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.05,0:43:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.62,0:43:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Harkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.12,0:43:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.62,0:43:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.12,0:43:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.65,0:43:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have said many times that only 0.4% of the world's population
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,ever gets to 540 or unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.65,0:43:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, true.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.65,0:43:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the world's population, though, that's 25 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.65,0:43:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good math.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.65,0:43:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.16,0:43:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet at 60 points higher, at 600, when you wrote Truth Versus Falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.16,0:43:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,there were only six people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.16,0:43:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes that 60 points higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.16,0:43:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.66,0:43:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.96,0:43:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what makes that 60 points of consciousness so extraordinarily hard
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.96,0:43:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that we start with 25 over one line and we only get six over another line?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.96,0:43:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To develop from 540 to 600?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.52,0:43:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.02,0:43:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's unconditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.02,0:43:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, sainthood is at 55-55.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.02,0:43:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.59,0:43:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.09,0:43:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love is 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.59,0:43:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That itself is extremely unusual, as you know, to 0.4%.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.76,0:44:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That, to go from there, means practicing spiritual principles
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.76,0:44:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.76,0:44:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.76,0:44:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.18,0:44:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.18,0:44:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It means very strict allegiance to spiritual pathway, truth, and techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.66,0:44:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with no variation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.66,0:44:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And it means mounting dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.66,0:44:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, from 540, saintliness is around 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.27,0:44:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, from there up, you encounter joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.99,0:44:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what joy is that, 580 or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.49,0:44:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that ecstasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.94,0:44:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, from there, you, having let go of all the things that are deterrents,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.74,0:44:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you go into a state of joy that is not the consequence of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.74,0:44:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the arising of an energy of the realization of the divinity of God
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.90,0:45:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,within as the source of one's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.57,0:45:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This, as you continue to surrender to it, continues on up, gets more than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.15,0:45:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and it becomes ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.15,0:45:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy is over 580, 585, 590, 595.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.04,0:45:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy is over 590.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.04,0:45:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy is very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.04,0:45:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy is 595, 998, anyway, 598.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.77,0:45:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The ecstasy itself is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.99,0:45:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot really be differentiated except by a sophisticated spiritual community
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.99,0:45:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,from maybe spiritual mania or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.99,0:45:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In this book, the last book, I wrote how to differentiate spiritual states from pathologic states.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.50,0:45:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from joy, which is relatively impossible to function in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.98,0:46:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you move to ecstasy, where it is impossible to function in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.36,0:46:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go to ecstasy, you go into a state that I cannot hardly describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.87,0:46:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It is ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.87,0:46:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you're tireless.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.87,0:46:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can dance forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.87,0:46:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can dance in front of the altar at midnight to the candlelight
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.00,0:46:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the ecstasy of the awareness of the presence of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.00,0:46:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can do that tirelessly, hour after hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.44,0:46:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to eat anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.67,0:46:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to drink anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.18,0:46:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.18,0:46:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are danced by the ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.18,0:46:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain symbols from ancient India come to your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.46,0:46:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity and its expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.55,0:47:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Hindu language and religion, culture has certain expressions and styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.68,0:47:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That state, you can become addicted to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.78,0:47:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The ecstasy is so ecstatic that the thought of existing without it is not even thinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.20,0:47:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then comes the knowingness in that extremely high state.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.04,0:47:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This, too, must be surrendered to the ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.04,0:47:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.24,0:47:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ecstasy is surrendered to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.88,0:47:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you come into the state of profound and infinite peace and bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.90,0:47:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely still, exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.60,0:47:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to eat, drink, breathe, or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.60,0:48:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the body survives or not is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.15,0:48:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're merely the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.88,0:48:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sat-cittananda.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.46,0:48:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,State of infinite bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.04,0:48:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The opportunity to leave, in fact, almost a beckoning to leave, is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.04,0:48:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people leave there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.29,0:48:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A few remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.92,0:48:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's very few, over 600, because of karmic propensity,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.79,0:48:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because of, I wouldn't say desire to leave, but the option to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.16,0:48:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I think there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.44,0:48:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget how many.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.88,0:48:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There were six.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.88,0:48:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.88,0:48:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, when you wrote your first book, there were 12 over 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.88,0:48:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But they leave, they leave, they leave, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, they only stay in that state for a certain length of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.94,0:49:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's been considerable periods of time when nobody over 600 was on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.20,0:49:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, six is quite a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.42,0:49:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.42,0:49:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Centuries go by with not a single enlightened sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.20,0:49:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see how rare they are throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.20,0:49:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take all the greatest sages of history,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.20,0:49:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,put them all together over a time track, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.20,0:49:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we always thought there were a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.26,0:49:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just hidden somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.26,0:49:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, they send off such an energy that they don't just remain suddenly hidden in a cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.55,0:49:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow it radiates out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.55,0:49:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.79,0:49:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.91,0:49:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The joy is surrendered to ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.91,0:49:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the ecstasy is surrendered to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.91,0:49:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know for what.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.91,0:49:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.91,0:49:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is the peace beyond all understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.91,0:50:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The peace of God, that's 600, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.39,0:50:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,On the last four charts that you showed,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.85,0:50:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it seemed to me like the consciousness on the left side was about 190,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.85,0:50:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and on the right side was about 290.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.85,0:50:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that the right side becomes another bunch of shoulds,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.36,0:50:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which then become limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.36,0:50:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems to me like you need to be neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.56,0:50:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like the self-forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.56,0:50:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.56,0:50:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about attractions and aversions?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.56,0:50:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.56,0:50:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.56,0:50:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems to me even on the right side of the chart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.56,0:50:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to be neutral to forgiving yourself or not forgiving yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.56,0:50:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a very high state.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.68,0:50:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.68,0:50:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.45,0:50:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.45,0:50:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.45,0:50:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.45,0:50:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.45,0:50:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.45,0:50:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.45,0:51:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.90,0:51:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.72,0:51:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.72,0:51:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.19,0:51:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who writes, beats up a book like this deserves a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.19,0:51:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the raggedy one I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.19,0:51:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.25,0:51:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the compliment, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.25,0:51:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.25,0:51:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.25,0:51:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the main thing is one time you said that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.53,0:51:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is the highest expression of divinity on this plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.53,0:51:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.92,0:51:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only one of the aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.92,0:51:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the highest?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.81,0:51:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say, see that's projecting the linear to the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.90,0:52:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is grace, there is love, there is divine order, harmony, infinite mercy, compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.25,0:52:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.32,0:52:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really say that one is higher than the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.32,0:52:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.32,0:52:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In a certain extent, they're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.32,0:52:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Different expressions of the same energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.32,0:52:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This way it looks like love, this way it looks like truth, this way it looks like compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.32,0:52:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this way it looks like forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.32,0:52:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, this way it's mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.64,0:52:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's only the same way of being, you know, type of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.37,0:52:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One is not really higher than the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.37,0:52:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can choose the option to try to approach enlightenment via one pathway or the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.88,0:52:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,which is more individual proclivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.08,0:52:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people are more heart people.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.62,0:52:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people would maybe go through the intellect and become Zen,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.62,0:52:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, go for Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.62,0:52:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Some would go through selfless service.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.62,0:53:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So the various yogas, selfless service, meditation, bhakti yoga,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.62,0:53:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,would be sort of personal proclivity, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.04,0:53:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And truth is always relative to the absolute?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.61,0:53:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.77,0:53:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's expression in this plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.47,0:53:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is relative to the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.47,0:53:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is relative, you know, relative to the absolute, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.47,0:53:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.81,0:53:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See a diamond, this way it looks that way, this way it looks this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.54,0:53:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all the same diamond, what do you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.54,0:53:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, compassion, mercy, omnipotence, omniscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.31,0:53:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just different facets of the diamond, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.31,0:53:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.24,0:53:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.24,0:53:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.24,0:53:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On the videos you've mentioned several times about the 91st Psalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.24,0:53:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.24,0:53:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I brought one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.24,0:53:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.24,0:54:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the internet and you probably could link to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.24,0:54:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.24,0:54:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I brought one just in case you wanted to make a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.24,0:54:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can link on your website.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.24,0:54:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.24,0:54:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a little bit crumpled from the airplane and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.24,0:54:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.24,0:54:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a bit crumpled.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.24,0:54:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So all of the questions that I had, you've already answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.24,0:54:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So every time I have a question at home, I watch a video and the answer comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.24,0:54:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.24,0:54:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have no questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.24,0:54:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's very good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.24,0:54:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet every, I'm constantly surrendering and talking to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.24,0:54:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.24,0:54:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.24,0:54:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.24,0:54:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.24,0:54:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.24,0:54:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.24,0:54:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.24,0:54:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.24,0:54:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.24,0:54:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.24,0:54:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.24,0:54:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.24,0:54:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.24,0:54:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.24,0:54:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.24,0:54:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.24,0:54:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.24,0:54:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some hopes, but then I surrendered them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.54,0:54:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had hopes of finding a husband, and then after eight years, I had to, I think that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.26,0:54:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody I met was undoing past karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.56,0:54:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a lot of .
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.93,0:55:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So again, I surrender even wanting a husband, but it would be very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.74,0:55:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.74,0:55:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.74,0:55:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then we'll get you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.74,0:55:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.74,0:55:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.74,0:55:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.74,0:55:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she should have what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.74,0:55:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweet, adorable lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.74,0:55:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, sweet, adorable ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.74,0:55:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.74,0:55:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You better get them while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.74,0:55:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.74,0:55:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.74,0:55:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.74,0:55:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know she'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.74,0:55:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.74,0:55:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.74,0:55:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.74,0:55:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.74,0:55:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.74,0:55:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.98,0:55:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.61,0:55:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for being available to us after your, this incredible work and all
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.61,0:55:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the reading I have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.61,0:55:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredible research.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.61,0:55:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very impressed about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.61,0:55:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a follower and the leader of spiritual group in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.61,0:55:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In where?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.61,0:55:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the spiritual groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.25,0:56:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.25,0:56:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the spiritual groups have been very helpful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.25,0:56:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.25,0:56:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.25,0:56:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.25,0:56:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.44,0:56:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.44,0:56:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.84,0:56:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way of a spiritual group, okay? It was Eckengard, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.76,0:56:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Eckengard. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.04,0:56:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.12,0:56:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, I have two or three questions. Can, when we have faith in a spiritual leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.26,0:56:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had the experience of grace of God many years ago, and I will never forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.30,0:56:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can, do you understand that? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.06,0:56:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll tell me what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.42,0:56:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.60,0:56:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Jackson. She tells me what people are saying all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.83,0:56:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that our faith could only lead us to this sense of grace of God and not the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.22,0:57:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we project the faith? Is it based on the grace of God or is it based on the leader of the group?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.59,0:57:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he's asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.55,0:57:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the grace of God. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.70,0:57:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.14,0:57:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,embody
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.54,0:57:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the level that you're at, will attract or be attracted to a teacher of that level, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.62,0:57:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But does my faith could make me feel the grace of God even if that leader could be not?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.78,0:57:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if the leader is not sufficient for you, then you'll be called away by another leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.90,0:57:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Somebody will say, you know, so-and-so and, you know, calibrate it and see where it's at, and
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.14,0:57:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then you go through. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.84,0:57:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little disillusion, but, in the end. I remember somebody saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.28,0:57:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, he's a great teacher, except he has no energy around the heart. Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.19,0:57:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we are followers, and I was a leader in my area, so are we limited to the level
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.75,0:58:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness, of the group, or we can transcend this level?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.11,0:58:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go to it. You'll go in accord of what you're attracted to and if you evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.19,0:58:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond it, you'll lose your interest and find something more exciting and more appropriate, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.19,0:58:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So staying could be a drag on my spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.19,0:58:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying might be a drag on that spiritual effort to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.19,0:58:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true. That's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.25,0:58:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know, when it's time to change, somehow it comes to you, it's time to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.25,0:58:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, even if I'm responsible with some people in my area, because I feel a bit responsible also, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.57,0:58:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take a little consultation to resolve what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.57,0:58:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about multiple issues now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.57,0:58:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Appropriateness of the teacher, the appropriateness of the group, and the appropriateness of your role, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.57,0:58:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.57,0:59:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay, thank you. You answered most of my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.15,0:59:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.15,0:59:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much again.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.15,0:59:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time to move on, it sort of comes in some way to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.15,0:59:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.40,0:59:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.40,0:59:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else begins to click.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.56,0:59:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he got involved with an Eckhart group, now he's lucky to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.56,0:59:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So nice to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.13,0:59:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.13,0:59:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering about praying for the dying. Is that a good practice? Or would it be helpful?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.92,0:59:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the admonition, pray ceaselessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.92,0:59:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pray all the time for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.92,0:59:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It is advantageous, we have permission to ask this, it is advantageous to pray for the dying, resist. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.99,0:59:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking because my mother seems to be in that process, and I don't know what, I don't really know how to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.99,1:00:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to praying for myself, you know, ask God for help for this and that, but not for other people, because I feel like I'm interfering.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.99,1:00:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.99,1:00:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're butting into their karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.99,1:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Like, how do I know what...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.99,1:00:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you ask for the highest good for this person and hold them alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.99,1:00:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we did when we did the Ohms, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.99,1:00:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.99,1:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's the highest good for these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.99,1:00:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.99,1:00:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe to crash in despair and say, dear God, I ask you, only you, no one else can, you know, in despair.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.34,1:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called hitting bottom. So many people find God through hitting bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.34,1:00:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take a typhoon, a hurricane, starvation, and being shot. Just as your body falls over, you got it. So who knows, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.94,1:00:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I found on the river doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.68,1:00:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I found on the river doing that, that beautiful Ohm prayer that I was holding in mind these people crying for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.68,1:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.68,1:00:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And could I have a different visualization be more beneficial? I mean, what could I...in my mind, I had an image of...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.68,1:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to control it. Just be who you are with it. Your intention is to help these people and pray for them. That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.68,1:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.68,1:01:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.28,1:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.70,1:01:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you saying thank you to the assistant. She didn't pray very good that time, did she?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.88,1:01:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you think she's got a scoreboard?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.36,1:01:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention is the goodwill to express unconditional love towards the people. That's sufficient. The intention is what does it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.36,1:01:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.36,1:01:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.36,1:01:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right to use the...to do the Ohm? Because I thought it was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.36,1:01:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do whatever you like. You can stand on your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.87,1:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, cranking a prayer wheel calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.87,1:01:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.87,1:01:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's the intention. It's not the mechanicalness. It's just a tin thing with things written on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.87,1:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.87,1:01:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.22,1:01:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention. You know, the intention of genuine reflection. The intention of prayerful hand-plast.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.28,1:02:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention is 540. So the intention of however you pray is sufficient. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.28,1:02:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like prayer helps...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.28,1:02:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop questioning and doubting about it. Just stop and do it at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.02,1:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make it complicated. You're making it complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.53,1:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.53,1:02:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You better see a priest. He'll tell you how to pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.60,1:02:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.60,1:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on page 342 here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.60,1:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called the prayer for the sick and dying. I can get you any prayer book. Look it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.60,1:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called prayer book. Prayers for the sick and dying. Prayers for the deceased.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.11,1:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good place to start.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.11,1:02:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take any of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.43,1:02:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get a prayer book?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.43,1:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.43,1:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got it listed. Prayers for the sick and dying. Prayers for certain people in surgery. Prayers for people in pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.31,1:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got prayers for specific things. So have a professional set up a prayer for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.58,1:02:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. One up for a dollar and a half. Twenty-two bucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.76,1:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you twenty-two bucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.76,1:03:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a prayer book.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.76,1:03:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.14,1:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Unity should help you too. I mean, you know, Unity has got prayer books for all that stuff. Don't you have a minister around you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.14,1:03:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't. I've never gone to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.14,1:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This lady needs a minister. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.14,1:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A soul that needs rescuing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.14,1:03:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.14,1:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm selling her for a dollar. Anybody can have her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.14,1:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's prayer groups. Like Unity has a prayer group.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.14,1:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.14,1:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a prayer book.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.14,1:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's other denominations.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.14,1:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a prayer book. Just an ordinary prayer book.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.14,1:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't know how to pray for them, then you can have a prayer group.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.14,1:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll tell you how. It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.14,1:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray book. So, you know, there's other...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.14,1:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary prayer book. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.14,1:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.24,1:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's people that will pray for your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.24,1:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop in the nearest hotel and look in the drawer next to the bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.61,1:03:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you, Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.61,1:03:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.61,1:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.85,1:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.98,1:04:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.98,1:04:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.98,1:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like I have selective surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.98,1:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things go away and stay away, and some seem to come back repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.04,1:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.04,1:04:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.84,1:04:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I surrender some things, they seem to go away and stay away, but others seem to come back over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.84,1:04:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Others come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.84,1:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So I was hoping...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.84,1:04:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.84,1:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.84,1:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When you surrender, it doesn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.84,1:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,True. So maybe you can go over the mechanics of surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.84,1:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should go over the mechanics of surrendering one more time because some of these things keep coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.84,1:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have to do it repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.84,1:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, I ask you to help me let go my attachment to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.32,1:04:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at what the payoff you're getting from clinging to it or what the aversion is to letting it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.32,1:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to look deeper within yourself to see what the obstruction is, the resistance is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.32,1:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things require repeated surrendering, repeated surrendering because it's a big stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.32,1:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.32,1:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a short stack of short duration, you can let it go with a few surrenders.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.32,1:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.32,1:05:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's a big one, a big one, you may have to do it over and over again and ask for God's help each time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.32,1:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then decide what is the quality of that which you're attached to.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.48,1:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.48,1:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.48,1:05:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.48,1:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the juice you're getting out of your attachment to the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.48,1:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're not willing to surrender, including feeling guilty that you haven't surrendered it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.94,1:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.94,1:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to look at the payouts on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.94,1:05:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.51,1:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things require persistence.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.51,1:05:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be persistent.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.51,1:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever got a spiritual counselor?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.88,1:05:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.24,1:05:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the trouble with today's world.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.24,1:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When we have a spiritual counselor, people really benefit from a spiritual counselor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.24,1:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They benefit from a spiritual confidant.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.40,1:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone with whom to bounce back things.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.84,1:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody really, in my view, needs a mentor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.84,1:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody really needs a confidant, a confessor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.84,1:06:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not Catholic, become one and go to confession.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.84,1:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.07,1:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody needs sort of a feedback.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.07,1:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 12-step groups, everybody has a sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.07,1:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody does it on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.48,1:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody shares what they're working through.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.48,1:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they get feedback from the older, wiser.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.48,1:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.87,1:06:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The mentor is sadly lacking in today's society.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.19,1:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody needs a mentor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.92,1:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a trusted older friend, confidant.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.92,1:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who you know has your best interest at heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.04,1:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.04,1:07:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can share their wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.12,1:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That helps you grow.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.12,1:07:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.67,1:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.08,1:07:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.08,1:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.74,1:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The bartender used to serve that assumption, but they...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.74,1:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against the union rules now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.74,1:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.74,1:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if he gives you advice and you take it and it doesn't work, you can sue the bartender.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.74,1:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So bartenders are no longer allowed to be spiritual counselors.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.09,1:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be a bartender.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.09,1:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bartender.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.09,1:07:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I frankly did give out the best advice I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.41,1:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.41,1:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because here's a fellow human being in trouble asking you, you know, for...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.41,1:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Feedback.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.41,1:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're just an ordinary human, you feel for the, you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.41,1:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not through sympathy, but through empathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.41,1:07:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it must feel like to have your wife leave you and get fired and all that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.31,1:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,all on the same day, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.31,1:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.59,1:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.59,1:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.59,1:08:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.59,1:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, I was recently listening to a lecture, a recorded lecture of the workshop, Intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.59,1:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.59,1:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.59,1:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the beginning, you said something to the effect that you are going to just tell
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.97,1:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,us what is going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.97,1:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're going to do in the workshop is you're going to just tell us what's going
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.97,1:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,on in the world, consciousness with the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.97,1:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And all you ask us to do is just pay attention and notice it, and that you don't want us
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.20,1:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.20,1:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm helping to...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.26,1:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can help me understand that without thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.26,1:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.12,1:08:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that in the video, Power of the Intention, that you told them that all you wanted them
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.12,1:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to do is sit back and listen and absorb it and not really think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.12,1:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.12,1:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.12,1:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.12,1:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.12,1:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.12,1:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.12,1:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I needed help.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.12,1:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.12,1:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.12,1:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.12,1:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.48,1:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.48,1:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.48,1:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.48,1:09:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.48,1:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.48,1:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.70,1:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it, that what you heard is imprinted as a frequency vibration in your aura.
