Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.13,1:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.13,1:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.80,1:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.97,1:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about thinking about it. No, he got it in his heart. He's conscious of the realization.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.40,1:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to say, you know, I love what you do and I love who you are
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.60,1:10:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't have a question and I want to cast a vote. I vote for you to, next year,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.48,1:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when you do this six times instead of doing half a day, to do a full day. That's my vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.76,1:10:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,His suggestion would serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.52,1:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His suggestion would serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.24,1:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll compromise. I'll talk for in the morning, but all afternoon will be spent with the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.88,1:11:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,group, conversation, being with each other, mingling, sharing, discussing, if we can arrange it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.40,1:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.20,1:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask if it
