Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.64,1:11:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves my highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.33,1:11:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves my highest good, to agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.91,1:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.79,1:11:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.66,1:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were going to get off your feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.26,1:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, I don't know. I'm always afraid. I'm afraid I'm being repetitious, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.79,1:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm repeating many of the same things again. I think other, you know, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.89,1:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.49,1:11:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.85,1:11:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what she said?
