Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.10,1:14:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,leading edge yeah yeah mm-hmm the leading edge is reporting to you what it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.75,1:14:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks is happening that's not what happening it's reporting to you what's
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.45,1:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not reporting you what's happening that's why you get bored with it I think
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.95,1:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to learn to quit thinking
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.01,1:14:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath the thinginess is an infinite silence right this instant I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.66,1:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,tuned into the silence nothing at all is happening do you like that no TV on no
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.42,1:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,dog barking no nothing going on yes what happens with that in that space basically
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.66,1:15:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.48,1:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.48,1:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's peaceful and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.48,1:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.48,1:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
