Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.37,1:16:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the cops or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.37,1:16:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.37,1:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say so to whatever conversation is going on, in or out, and live in the silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.56,1:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why people say it doesn't bother me is I haven't in this life paid any attention
