Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.41,1:17:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.94,1:17:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, people try to jerk you around and play you with their drama.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.94,1:17:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you refuse the drama game, you can live in a peaceful silence and the whole thing's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.94,1:17:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,amusing.
