Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.12,1:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,gives you a chance to progress, and it gives you a chance to progress, and it gives you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.12,1:21:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a chance to progress, and it gives you a chance to progress, and it gives you a chance to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.12,1:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,progress, and it gives you a chance to progress, and it gives you a chance to progress, and
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.12,1:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be more alert not to get in your own way
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.08,1:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or not let those obstacles come up
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.56,1:21:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that you were talking about this morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.56,1:21:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you say the disturbance comes up,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.78,1:21:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to look at what is the disturbance
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.30,1:21:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and why the disturbance is going on,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.94,1:22:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and you work on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.22,1:22:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that will disappear,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.52,1:22:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and life will be happy and cheerful and chipper,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.66,1:22:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can sing songs,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.60,1:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the next thing will come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.90,1:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.66,1:22:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's a long process.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.58,1:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a growth process.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.54,1:22:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a process.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.36,1:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.26,1:22:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate so much what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.58,1:22:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.14,1:22:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.37,1:22:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a lifelong process.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.34,1:22:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When it gets to be so nice like that, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.82,1:22:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't it stay that way?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.37,1:22:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.70,1:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask one quick question before my main question?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.81,1:22:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Before what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.95,1:22:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The main question.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.25,1:22:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.67,1:22:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.93,1:22:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In your 1996 video, Power Versus Force,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.58,1:22:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you had this blonde that helped you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.80,1:22:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you teach me how to enter into her field
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.08,1:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and do anything I'm going to have to do to get out of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.36,1:22:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a blonde in that video.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.22,1:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.78,1:23:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know how to enter into her field.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.50,1:23:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean by enter into her field.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.60,1:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a telephone number or a...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.30,1:23:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know who he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.60,1:23:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see her in the audience here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.90,1:23:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is your real question?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.52,1:23:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.74,1:23:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.26,1:23:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.95,1:23:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm involved in three areas of research and practice now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.75,1:23:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One is using the mind mirror to look at brain waves patterns.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.46,1:23:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Another is using genograms for family constellation work.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.05,1:23:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And the third is I'm a Western and Vedic astrologer
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.31,1:23:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to integrate the two disciplines into a higher astrology.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.63,1:23:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In your book, Truth and Falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.73,1:23:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrated astrology, I think, between 205 and 410,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.29,1:23:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and is it possible to create a higher astrology?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.05,1:23:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There are various levels of astrology.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.41,1:24:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When people talk about astrology,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.93,1:24:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not talking about just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.93,1:24:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the astrology in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.17,1:24:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That calibrates the lowest sort of pop astrology.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.86,1:24:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's astrology based on more ancient wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.36,1:24:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which really is going beyond astrology,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.52,1:24:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at contextual understandings.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.80,1:24:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a linear causality anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.30,1:24:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.42,1:24:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that when I said that the consciousness level of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.82,1:24:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,went from 190 to 205,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.25,1:24:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that was about at the time the harmonic concordance,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.77,1:24:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but not caused by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.89,1:24:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, in November of what was it,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.15,1:24:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,203, we were in San Francisco,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.57,1:24:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it went from 205 to 207.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.87,1:24:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That was again at the time of,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.89,1:24:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm using the correct terminology,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.97,1:24:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,harmonic concordance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.75,1:24:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.91,1:24:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So aligned with that, at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.01,1:24:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because if the universe is doing this,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.51,1:25:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then these things are both moving as a consequence of this,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.35,1:25:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,not because this is causing this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.09,1:25:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.71,1:25:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The understanding and the astrological sign
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.43,1:25:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,are appearing because they are both being swung this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.65,1:25:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.15,1:25:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not causing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.43,1:25:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is concomitant.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.57,1:25:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often the ego confuses concomitant with causal.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.81,1:25:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to present astrology
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.93,1:25:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in a new context so it has a higher calibration?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.21,1:25:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.63,1:25:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be significance and meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.68,1:25:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The limitation of astrology as I see it is causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.47,1:25:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your job because the moon is going over your backyard.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.33,1:25:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.16,1:25:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.66,1:25:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That constellation is not causing anything here at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.66,1:25:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you move beyond duality,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.44,1:25:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you could move it to a higher...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.16,1:26:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Astrology could work out as,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.38,1:26:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, a concordance in which you pick up rhythms
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.28,1:26:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which are the consequence of greater rhythms,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.78,1:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or the consequence of even greater rhythms.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.92,1:26:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually you reach the mind of God
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.56,1:26:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who will tell you to forget about astrology.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.84,1:26:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What about brain wave patterns?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.00,1:26:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.92,1:26:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it worthwhile to pursue?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.26,1:26:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on what context.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.96,1:26:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at brain wave patterns of people at different disciplines
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.80,1:26:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and different levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.86,1:26:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And different accomplishments and different contributions?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.94,1:26:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.32,1:26:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be some kind of research.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.60,1:26:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the purpose would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.67,1:26:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To find out different skills.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.27,1:26:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole area of brain research
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.65,1:26:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is emerging rather rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.15,1:26:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd have to know more about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.21,1:26:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost track of where it's at right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.16,1:26:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.54,1:27:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it takes this moment to express my deepest love
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.62,1:27:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and gratitude to God and to God's teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.80,1:27:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.50,1:27:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.86,1:27:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in the last few months, my life has changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.50,1:27:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.89,1:27:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The first question is about the calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.08,1:27:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,on the transcendental meditations.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.47,1:27:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcendental meditations?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.05,1:27:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,TM.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.91,1:27:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.25,1:27:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.55,1:27:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is very low.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.57,1:27:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 200, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.82,1:27:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I read some of their material.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.19,1:27:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They are practicing, you know, promote peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.45,1:27:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.65,1:27:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.96,1:27:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is, why is the TM calibrated so low?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.14,1:27:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by so low?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.28,1:27:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the number?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.18,1:28:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like 200-something on your slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.08,1:28:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.98,1:28:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,200 is...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.68,1:28:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is 200 or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.80,1:28:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.76,1:28:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.60,1:28:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't created by the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.18,1:28:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.19,1:28:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.74,1:28:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in my mind, I thought it should be higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.02,1:28:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So the second question is about the jaya,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.56,1:28:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the jaya hypothesis, is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.56,1:28:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaya hypothesis?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.56,1:28:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.56,1:28:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.56,1:28:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.56,1:28:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth is a living organism.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.56,1:28:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.56,1:28:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you share some light on this?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.56,1:28:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates as negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.56,1:28:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear it breathing...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.87,1:28:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a fantasy or a reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.87,1:28:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is jaya a living organism?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.44,1:28:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My understanding is that it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.44,1:28:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.44,1:28:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.44,1:28:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to you to ask for your calibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.44,1:28:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.44,1:28:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.44,1:28:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.04,1:28:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.04,1:28:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.46,1:28:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.46,1:28:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.46,1:28:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.46,1:28:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.46,1:28:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.46,1:28:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.46,1:28:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.46,1:28:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.46,1:28:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.46,1:28:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.46,1:29:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me theting of what you're calibrating?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.46,1:29:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want me to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.46,1:29:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.46,1:29:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to calibrate the concept of your...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.96,1:29:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permitted to calibrate the concept of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.76,1:29:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.98,1:29:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.04,1:29:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.04,1:29:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we gotta know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.54,1:29:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot calibrate it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.54,1:29:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't calibrate it right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.04,1:29:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.04,1:29:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a concept.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.04,1:29:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.39,1:29:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it, what difference does it make you is what I wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.89,1:29:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I come from the science background.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.39,1:29:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.39,1:29:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but then recently after studying your teachings, I feel like I made the transition to the nonlinear domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.39,1:29:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.39,1:29:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of this, I see that there was a merging between science and spirituality,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.39,1:29:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I see the Gaia hypothesis actually bring an opportunity to this endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.38,1:29:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels that the Gaia...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.38,1:29:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gaia is a living single organism, is the concept, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.38,1:29:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.64,1:30:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaia means that all that exists as the Earth is one single unit. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.37,1:30:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.37,1:30:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the same karma as the bacteria, the octopus, the snake, the fish, the killer, the bandit, the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.14,1:30:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you share the same karma with all of them? Are you one with them?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.81,1:30:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.81,1:30:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then by your own definition, you are. They'll have to serve you where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.84,1:30:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you caused all that disaster?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.36,1:30:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In New Orleans, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.36,1:30:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we will learn something from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.90,1:30:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we learned something from it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.25,1:30:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.51,1:30:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.96,1:30:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the value of holding the concept of Gaia? What is the value of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.95,1:30:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.95,1:30:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As a scientist, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.95,1:31:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Personally, I feel like the science is hitting a wall, and it's convergence of these two domains may bring a new consciousness to our being.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.17,1:31:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a working concept.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.17,1:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a useful concept, yes. Whether it's a self-existent reality or something else, but it certainly is a useful concept. You treat the whole thing as if it's one. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.80,1:31:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it bring more unity consciousness by advocating this?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.18,1:31:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know. We don't know if it's going to bring unity.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.24,1:31:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're free to hold your concept about what the world is and what it means and what its significance is, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.24,1:31:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it depends on age, sophistication, education, many things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.20,1:31:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.20,1:31:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.20,1:31:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't calibrate it so we can't go any further with it. We've got to know that...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.66,1:31:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useful to him. It's useful to him right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.66,1:31:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's useful to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.66,1:31:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.20,1:32:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.24,1:32:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.13,1:32:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard that concept in a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.13,1:32:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gaia?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.13,1:32:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mm-hmm. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.95,1:32:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. You have described the experience energetically of the high 500s.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.78,1:32:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And specifically the energy as it travels up the spine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.78,1:32:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Kind of leaning in. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.78,1:32:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As this intense, exquisite experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.78,1:32:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.78,1:32:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it always present in that way in the high 500s?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.78,1:32:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is always anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.84,1:32:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.84,1:32:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Characteristically, that's how it is. That's how experienced it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.84,1:32:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.84,1:32:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Very exquisite, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.84,1:32:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And specifically up the spinal column like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.91,1:32:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.91,1:32:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was experientially. It flowed up the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.91,1:32:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.91,1:33:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And into the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.91,1:33:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.91,1:33:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you thought of the left side of the brain, it poured into the left side of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.91,1:33:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you thought of the right side of the brain, it poured into the right side of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.91,1:33:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it came down and began to go out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.91,1:33:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.20,1:33:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.20,1:33:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you shut your eyes, it got even more intense.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.20,1:33:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.20,1:33:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to just formulate another question.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.85,1:33:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there are times when I feel...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.52,1:33:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember as a kid watching Sylvester the Cat, I think, in cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.52,1:33:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And his tail would go into the outlet and he would fry with electricity.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.52,1:33:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need me to repeat it? No?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.00,1:33:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she'll have to tell me what to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.00,1:33:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.09,1:33:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are times when I experience that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.22,1:33:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to understand is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.22,1:34:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a resistance?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.76,1:34:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean like an energy surge is what you feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.76,1:34:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.76,1:34:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.76,1:34:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really a surge.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.76,1:34:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,More just like a huge overload.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.76,1:34:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.76,1:34:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And trying to understand is it resistance?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.76,1:34:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.76,1:34:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.76,1:34:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.63,1:34:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if you just continuously surrender to it and let it be whatever it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.63,1:34:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then it seems to spread out more and dissipate.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.20,1:34:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.20,1:34:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, like I'll need to lay down on the floor sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.20,1:34:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.20,1:34:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes after 10 or 15 minutes of that...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.20,1:34:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You just surrender to it no matter what form or expression it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.06,1:34:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.09,1:34:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.09,1:34:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.09,1:34:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and you ask God for, you know, understanding and revelation of its meaning and significance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.38,1:35:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All those things, I've found, just don't resist them.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.11,1:35:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one usually evolves into something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.11,1:35:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.11,1:35:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about it, because it's gonna stay anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.11,1:35:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.11,1:35:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.11,1:35:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.11,1:35:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's transitional, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.11,1:35:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.73,1:35:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.73,1:35:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.92,1:35:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.92,1:35:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in a hospital, and I'm exposed, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.05,1:35:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surrounded by viruses and bacteria, and they calibrated a one.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.56,1:35:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.43,1:35:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, there just seems to be a lot of attention within the healthcare system.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.64,1:35:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.64,1:35:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.64,1:35:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.64,1:35:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.64,1:35:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.64,1:35:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.64,1:35:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.64,1:35:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.64,1:35:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.64,1:35:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.64,1:35:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.87,1:35:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.87,1:35:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.87,1:35:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.87,1:35:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.87,1:35:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm also within the health system that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.16,1:35:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.16,1:35:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.16,1:35:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working in a hospital, is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.16,1:35:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.16,1:35:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.16,1:35:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.16,1:35:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And there seems to be a lot of attention, if a virus and bacteria calibrated a one...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.16,1:35:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.16,1:35:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a lot of attention paid to something that calibrates at a one.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.16,1:35:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.32,1:36:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving it a lot of power, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.00,1:36:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have that much power, or are we just giving it the power?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.32,1:36:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't have power.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.32,1:36:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have power.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.32,1:36:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.64,1:36:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, pneumonia isn't real?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.64,1:36:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.64,1:36:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.64,1:36:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.64,1:36:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,using force and power. And it's not the bacteria, it's the body's reaction to it, yeah? You're
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.78,1:36:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,confusing power and force. Bin Laden calibrates at 20, and 9-11 is the consequence. So you
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.91,1:36:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,see what I'm saying? That which is by virtue of its form is destructive, not by virtue
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.91,1:36:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of its power.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.88,1:36:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So just by, like it calibrates at a 1. So just being at a 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.46,1:36:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacteria are at a 1 as far as their level of consciousness, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.62,1:36:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a tack, a tack doesn't calibrate very high, but under the tire of your car,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.16,1:37:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't that it has the power to destroy your life, you understand? It's just the consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.60,1:37:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of its linear characteristics. A nail in the road, and your tire hits it, now you can
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.29,1:37:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,turn over. So you're misconceiving it, you're misconceptualizing it by saying, look, the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.10,1:37:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,nail has the power to kill five people in the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.44,1:37:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.68,1:37:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a metal game you're playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.92,1:37:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not all viruses are bad, either. Some viruses are...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.66,1:37:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, but I get what she's saying. She's misconceiving power.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.42,1:37:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.18,1:37:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have the power.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.44,1:37:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it just seems we focus a lot of attention on it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.46,1:37:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, we do with nails in the tires, too. I sweep them out of my driveway all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.30,1:37:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.24,1:37:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand her question. It comes up once in a while. Because of the form, say.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.25,1:37:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for your books and your work, and it's been a great deal to me, and
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.07,1:38:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that. I have a question, and I'm not sure how to ask it, so I'll just talk
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.49,1:38:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,around it, and hopefully it'll come out in some meaningful way. One of your helpers said
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.66,1:38:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to ask you personally because you don't answer email very much, so I figured
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.98,1:38:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd come up and ask the question. It has to do with the calibration charts and...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.78,1:38:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a walking email, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.98,1:38:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.28,1:38:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they walk around in a human body. They'll do anything to get their... Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.76,1:38:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't press the delete button. The calibration charts were... On one level, they make a great
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.09,1:38:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,deal of sense. In other words, I can tell that certain levels have more energy than
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.67,1:38:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,others, and it just makes a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.49,1:38:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can intuit it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.49,1:38:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. My question has to do with how accurate is this depending on what one's level is,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.01,1:38:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.01,1:38:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher your level, the more accurate it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.01,1:39:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. I'm finding that, for example, within a circle of friends, there'll be just a wild
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.01,1:39:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,range of interpretations about, well, I'm obviously a 600. I'm below 600. I'm below...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.89,1:39:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody else had that experience? I don't know, but it just seems to be whoever's doing
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.22,1:39:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the interpreting is going to be higher and higher and higher depending on where they're
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.74,1:39:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.74,1:39:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.74,1:39:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seems to me that there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.74,1:39:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look, it comes with wisdom and experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.62,1:39:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.14,1:39:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell people, don't bother calibrating yourself, because you're not going to get an accurate
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.94,1:39:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,number. Besides, it's irrelevant. When it doesn't mean anything to you anymore, you'll
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.64,1:39:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.47,1:39:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the questions I have was this misinterpretation of the different calibration levels. Maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.53,1:39:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't do it back then, but something along that line, which led to the caste system
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.89,1:39:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in India, for example.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.89,1:39:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which led to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.89,1:39:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something where...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.89,1:39:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The caste.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.89,1:39:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The caste system.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.89,1:39:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The caste.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.97,1:39:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The caste system.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.04,1:39:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you're labeling people, like, they're untouchables here, or this person's a merchant,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.19,1:39:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this person's a private level, that type of thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.19,1:40:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.19,1:40:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.19,1:40:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that the misuse of such a calibration could lead to something like
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.19,1:40:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.19,1:40:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The misuse of anything, including holy water, can drown you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.19,1:40:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.19,1:40:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It can drown in holy water. Babies do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.19,1:40:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing this baby. I had to run to the bathroom for a second. I come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.19,1:40:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.19,1:40:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.19,1:40:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.19,1:40:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.19,1:40:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.19,1:40:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.19,1:40:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.19,1:40:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.19,1:40:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.19,1:40:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.19,1:40:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.38,1:40:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.38,1:40:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's floating in the christening thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.80,1:40:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that answers my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.84,1:40:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What can be done with truth in what way. You know what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.18,1:40:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Back...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.48,1:40:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.48,1:40:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's misused or abused you know. But you're mixing classes now. Categories.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.22,1:40:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just thinking in Sedona a million years from now when they unearth
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.58,1:40:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.28,1:41:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Hawkinology, you know, and find that this work existed, and trying to make something out of it, I was wondering how they're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.28,1:41:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of ology?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.28,1:41:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawkinology.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.28,1:41:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.28,1:41:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawkinology.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.28,1:41:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawkinology.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.28,1:41:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll leave some relics.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.28,1:41:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.28,1:41:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean they'll still be here?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.28,1:41:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.28,1:41:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands of future generations can verify them.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.28,1:41:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been working on a book, actually, for ten years, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.28,1:41:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing kinesiology for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.28,1:41:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to ask your permission to use some of your writing in the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.28,1:41:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just send me the quotes you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.28,1:41:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.28,1:41:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll give you formal permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.28,1:41:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.28,1:41:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.28,1:41:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.28,1:41:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.69,1:41:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawkinology.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.69,1:41:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.69,1:41:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.69,1:41:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.69,1:41:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it's the intention with which you use it that determines the result.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.36,1:41:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.64,1:41:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.64,1:41:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.64,1:41:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.64,1:41:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.64,1:41:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.64,1:42:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you expand a little bit on the...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.64,1:42:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you expand a little more on intention?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.64,1:42:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the mechanics of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.64,1:42:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.64,1:42:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.64,1:42:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.64,1:42:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter how long you hold the thought or from what level it comes from?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.64,1:42:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, intention means what your purpose, your goal is.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.64,1:42:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.84,1:42:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, if your intention or your goal is to disprove kinesiology, you can do it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.84,1:42:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.84,1:42:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How many pennies have I got in my pocket?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.84,1:42:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.84,1:42:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I heard that?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.84,1:42:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If your intention is to learn, you see, you can tell right away the intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.25,1:42:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One is a declaration, one is a denomination, the other one is a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.35,1:42:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell right away before they even open their mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.64,1:42:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This person asks a question, this person makes a negative declaration.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.64,1:42:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.64,1:42:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to understand something, you go to the man, the best person who can understand
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.08,1:43:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it, the best person who knows about it, and you ask them about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.36,1:43:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.36,1:43:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.36,1:43:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.42,1:43:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.42,1:43:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people complicate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.42,1:43:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why they complicate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.42,1:43:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I also would like to extend an invitation to you from Mary Olmwake and the Unity Church
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.42,1:43:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of Kahului in Maui to come visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.42,1:43:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Maui.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.42,1:43:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maui, well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.42,1:43:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a good swimmer?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.42,1:43:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a good swimmer?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.42,1:43:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can make it all the way to Hawaii, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.42,1:43:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.42,1:43:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.42,1:43:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.42,1:43:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.42,1:43:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.42,1:43:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.42,1:43:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.42,1:43:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.96,1:43:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been in Hawaii since World War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.96,1:43:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I went out through Pearl and I came back through Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.96,1:43:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan's been to Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.96,1:43:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.96,1:43:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a daughter there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.96,1:43:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Might be doing school there next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.25,1:43:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.25,1:43:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.25,1:43:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.25,1:43:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.25,1:43:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we finish it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.25,1:43:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.25,1:43:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.25,1:43:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.25,1:43:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pleasure and such a joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.50,1:43:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're God's gift to me, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.50,1:43:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.50,1:43:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.50,1:43:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.50,1:43:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.54,1:44:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.78,1:44:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.78,1:44:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.78,1:44:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.78,1:44:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.78,1:44:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.78,1:44:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.78,1:44:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.81,1:44:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.81,1:44:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.81,1:44:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.81,1:44:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.81,1:44:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.84,1:44:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.84,1:44:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.84,1:44:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.84,1:44:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.84,1:44:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the divine presence in the form of these magnificent people.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.84,1:44:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And we do again, hold in mind, those in need of the love, the feeling of the presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.58,1:44:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because you can go through anything, anything when you feel the presence within
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.50,1:44:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you, any kind of agony, any kind of forgiveness, so we pray that the people who need it feel
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.88,1:44:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the strength of God's love.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.08,1:44:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength of God's love.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.88,1:44:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody thinks of God's love as a set of flowers and we'll sing pretty songs.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.84,1:44:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.46,1:44:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.57,1:45:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In a snowbank, everything stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.69,1:45:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of divinity was overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.39,1:45:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.51,1:45:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Melted.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.62,1:45:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It melts with its infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.15,1:45:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exquisitely gentle.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.49,1:45:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Exquisitely soft and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.15,1:45:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Simultaneously, infinitely powerful like ultra steel.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.68,1:45:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to experience it to understand what seems like an ambiguity.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.02,1:45:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be soft, ultra gentle?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.85,1:45:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So exquisite that it melts.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.84,1:45:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Melts one.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.56,1:45:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time of infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.70,1:45:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like a strange paradox.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.63,1:45:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have been there will tell you that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.57,1:45:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Exquisitely sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.29,1:45:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentle.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.73,1:45:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.59,1:45:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.60,1:45:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And of infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.71,1:46:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what the people need.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.79,1:46:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.03,1:46:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.69,1:46:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.00,1:46:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.53,1:46:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.66,1:46:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.60,1:46:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they find this lovely, uh, did Gabe find this?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.05,1:46:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot who found this pillow.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.63,1:46:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabe, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.21,1:46:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Gabe there?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.23,1:46:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.59,1:46:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.55,1:46:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see where he was.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.31,1:46:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.43,1:46:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Gabe there?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.16,1:46:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's Gabe.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.84,1:46:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know where he got this pillow.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.42,1:46:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this go, Gabe?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.72,1:46:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.72,1:46:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.89,1:46:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.87,1:46:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we had another day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.13,1:46:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.49,1:46:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
